# Social URL Test Cases

Real chat examples containing social media URLs for scraping.

## TikTok

### Accordion Video
- **URL:** `https://vt.tiktok.com/ZS6myoDYu/`
- **Resolves to:** `https://www.tiktok.com/@sergey.sadovoy/video/7455066896669461782`
- **Content:** Accordion/music performance
- **Chat context:**
```
[1/9/25, 7:08:05 PM] Masha Broadbent: Maybe I should learn this instrument next?  Or cooking…

https://vt.tiktok.com/ZS6myoDYu/
[1/9/25, 7:08:20 PM] Masha Broadbent: I love cooking
```


11618-[4/7/25, 7:42:30 PM] Masha Broadbent: Must buy some stock
11619-
11620:https://vt.tiktok.com/ZSrUpUkR7/

(look up the video, see that it's about the stock market and investing advice)

## Generic Websites (OG tags)

### Travel Blog - Urupukapuka Island
- **URL:** `https://www.neverendingvoyage.com/urupukapuka-island-new-zealand/`
- **Content:** Travel blog post about island in Bay of Islands, NZ
- **Chat context:**
```
[10/21/25, 7:48:42 AM] Masha Broadbent: https://www.neverendingvoyage.com/urupukapuka-island-new-zealand/

I wanna go there!
[10/21/25, 7:51:40 AM] Masha Broadbent: We can take a water taxi, a boat or drive via Opua car ferry
```
- **Why it's perfect:** Clear activity suggestion with follow-up travel details
